By":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:45:27.000Z","msg":"其實唔可以咁簡單話我地輸左，你睇埋我地既回應先。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ISOCHK/photos/a.10150095899775676/10158221665585676/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FISOCHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.10150095899775676%2F10158221665585676%2F&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYc2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=17f06c91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ISOCHK/photos/a.10150095899775676/10158221665585676/</a><br />\n<br />\n對我地既回應有問題可以去呢度問<br />\n<br />\n眾籌覆核政府禁制網上言論 - 你問我答<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ngdtqJX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ngdtqJX</a>"},{"pid":"3bc37066dfdcb17d19dd0cb0d688f1d32de8764d","tid":1723570,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ba15502fa83aecf71cfca3175108a64621e7155","tid":1723570,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"我地要守護法庭 捍衛法治<br />\n破壞法庭就係破壞法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:30:32.000Z","msg":"做乜講埋我個句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a8a8679a64f6c55c473052dfd479b1781cab5c","tid":1723570,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b3f8b04e9c493f10a3eea7aa5daf32f2049ace1","tid":1723570,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:43:06.000Z","msg":"當法官正式用行動宣傳三權合作，我等平民將無需捍衛三權分立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:45:55.000Z","msg":"三權分立，司法獨立係用於保障人民<br />\n<br />\n分權的目的在於避免獨裁者的產生。古代的皇帝以至地方官員均集立法、執法（行政）、司法三大權於一身，容易造成權力的濫用。即使在現代，立法、運用稅款的權力通常掌握在代表人民意願的議會中，司法權的獨立在於防止執法機構濫權。<span style=\"color: red;\">同時各種權力由於在行使的過程中獨立於其他公權力之外</span>，不會受到其他權力所帶來的干擾，使權利的行使有了一定的靈活性，一定程度上可以為國家的運行提高效率。<br />\n<br />\nJudicial independence is the concept that the judiciary should be independent from the other branches of government. That is, courts should not be subject to improper influence from the other branches of government or from private or partisan interests. Judicial independence is important to the idea of separation of powers.<br />\n<br />\n獨立係指獨立於公權力，係香港俾法人扭曲為獨立於人民嘅監察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}